### Idea submission request for students per their group and only group members can make it
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/ideas/submit/ HTTP/1/1
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Smart Waste Management System",
    "broad_area": "IoT and Smart Cities",
    "objective": "To develop an IoT-based waste monitoring system for optimized garbage collection.",
    "originality_innovativeness": "Uses smart sensors and AI-based route optimization for garbage trucks.",
    "key_activities": "Deploy sensors in waste bins, create a real-time dashboard, integrate AI for route planning.",
    "data_sources": "IoT sensors, government waste reports, GPS data.",
    "technology_usage": "Raspberry Pi, Python, GPS, Google Maps API, Django.",
    "scalability": "Can be deployed in cities worldwide to reduce waste management costs.",
    "social_impact": "Enhances cleanliness and improves waste collection efficiency."
}

### Idea submission freezed by admin user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/groups/freeze/ HTTP/1/1
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: application/json

### Students can view their group details (members & submitted ideas)
